5dc890088f6de6c8ac43ce840fa1f579914","tid":1964120,"uid":238862,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ef5d04436f25120c45757351a01fae6fb7b3c96e","tid":1964120,"uid":235100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b826316d2f2a802b65521d1cd754db6be4dd9122","tid":1964120,"uid":238862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T07:02:03.000Z","msg":"養緊龍貓 <br />\n依家先養咗半個月<br />\n聽日佢就三個月大<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T07:14:33.000Z","msg":"我都想由bb養起！ching邊度買翻嚟有bb揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我見旺角嗰啲好似全部都好大隻咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T07:19:07.000Z","msg":"Fb 搵龍貓領養gp<br />\n有啲會係賣有啲會係領養<br />\n旺角有好多都係一歲內或者一歲半<br />\n睇落去好大隻但其實佢嗰啲全部都好瘦<br />\n係啲毛好厚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"403142e700b393d97c633f9b239ee2f39472ee5d","tid":1964120,"uid":238862,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T07:36:01.000Z","msg":"順帶一提<br />\n啲人話養仔仔好啲<br />\n仔仔就親人啲<br />\n囡囡就高竇啲<br />\n因為龍貓係母系社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPs:我嗰隻係仔仔 依家差唔多可以任摸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bb308b02211952cb96774ed724231a58ab3a19c","tid":1964120,"uid":252720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d494a65180cfe7406c2773077c5530e05adaadd0","tid":1964120,"uid":235100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70159de7b75a9dbc4b7081f701a3b8eea87dc5bd","tid":1964120,"uid":252720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c752e9859c328edbd8b14c3bb6893f5fe33ac1a4","tid":1964120,"uid":235100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T21